title: #171 - Jeff Dye & ME
description: Comedian Jeff Dye & I hang out in the Mancave & talk about past managers, my theory on the "comics' spirit", our constitutions, hi-jinx, The Vanderjagt Jersey, his tour w/ Brandt Tobler, Alt Comics vs. Bro Comics, & working on television.
